.DT
add_only_respond_to
Disk World creator help
add_only_respond_to

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_only_respond_to -  This adds an object into the list of objects that we will only respond to.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_only_respond_to(object person)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^person%^RESET%^ - the person to add to the response array

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/response_mon.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This adds an object into the list of objects that we will only respond
to.  If this array is empty then we will respond to anyone, if it has
something in it then we will only respond to them.
.EP

